<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.5.7">
<l>teṉṉa vaṉtamar ceppami lātār</l>
<l rend="indent">cēva takkuvār pōlapu kuntu</l>
<l>piṉṉum vaṉkayiṟ ṟālpiṇit teṟṟip</l>
<l rend="indent">piṉmuṉ ṉākavi ḻuppataṉ muṉṉam</l>
<l>iṉṉa vaṉiṉai yāṉeṉṟu colli</l>
<l rend="indent">yeṇṇi yuḷḷamai yiruḷaṟa nōkki</l>
<l>maṉṉa vaṉmatu cūtaṉa ṉeṉpār</l>
<l rend="indent">vāṉa kattumaṉ ṟāṭikaḷ tāmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[If you are] looking to end the darkness in [your] heart,</l>
<l rend="indent">thinking [of him], saying “He is such a One”,</l>
<l>before the crooked servants of Yama</l>
<l rend="indent">come like those who drive oxen,</l>
<l rend="indent">kicking and tying [you] up with strong rope</l>
<l rend="indent">and then dragging [you] back and forth</l>
<l>—[take note that] those who say “King Madhusūdana”</l> 
<l rend="indent">are the intermediaries of heaven.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
